&lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please add your name to the waitlist below.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;When applications open, we will be in touch with next steps.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
