&lt;li&gt;Successful completion of the editing test will be followed by a short volunteer training, again on your schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upon completion of training, you will review and submit loans on your own. Please remember the 2-hour-per-week commitment.&lt;/li&gt;
