&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Managing volunteers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working with or managing geographically distributed teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
